---
description: Forbidden patterns in this repository
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Forbidden patterns:
- UI directly executing Git commands
- business logic hidden inside JSX render branches
- storing async query data in multiple conflicting stores
- raw process output used as frontend contract
- shell command strings built by concatenation with user input
- free-form AI output trusted without validation
- broad rewrites unrelated to the task
- placeholder implementations merged as if complete
- silent catch blocks
- unsafe destructive defaults
- architecture leakage between layers
- giant god-components for multi-panel workflows
- parser logic mixed with command execution logic